limiting
opportunities; and,
 sustainability risks for new social enterprises.
The SWOT analysis provides a useful way of briefly summarising the current situation, some of the
ways forward, and some of the issues. In this way it provides a useful point of reflection prior to policy
recommendations in the next chapter.
